\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 Raven thought over all kinds of plans for getting this light into the world and finally he hit on a good one. The rich man living there had a daughter, and he thought, \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93I will make myself very small and drop into the water in the form of a small piece of dirt.\u8221\'94 The girl swallowed this dirt and became pregnant. When her time was completed, they made a hole for her, as was customary, in which she was to bring forth, and lined it with rich furs of all sorts. But the child did not wish to be born on those fine things. Then its grandfather felt sad and said, \u8220\'93What do you think it would be best to put into that hole? Shall we put in moss?\u8221\'94 So they put moss inside and the baby was born on it. Its eyes were very bright and moved around rapidly.}{ }
